title: 2021 NFL Trade Deadline Primer
description:
Nora and Mal each provide three trade scenarios, from likely to unlikely, and a move that a team should not make at the deadline.
Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin

Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
